	     <tr><td id=headerrow colspan=2 class=mform valign=top><a name=item.html?item=4192&mid=105610015016499>&nbsp;</a><a id=sj href=item.html?item=4192&mid=105610015016499>Love it</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=4192&mid=105610015016499#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a>
	     <br clear=all><small>Posted @ Fri, Jun 20th 5:50 AM 2003</small></td></tr>
	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=228021><span id= >Anarus</span></a><br><span id=notbold>15 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>This is what I know.&nbsp;&nbsp;Hits for 3 waves of 125.  Has a MR modifier of -100.  Is AE and procs quite offten.  Even with a 160+ MR I get hit with it 7 out of 10 times.  Droped in arena for me, don't remember the name of the mob.  I love using this when I get adds, or I accedently overpull.  I can take out SEVERAL mobs with the combination of a good DS and this sword.  I always tell my healer Don't heal me unless I am about dead (unless of course I have LoH) untill the weapon procs.  After the weapon procs, I have had lvl 60 monks TRY to take agro from me, and have been unable to.  With the way this weapon has proced for me, with shammy buffs, I almost have a continuous 125 AE dot.  I still have plans on picking up some more MR gear, and getting together with a few other tanks and such, and have an AE party.  All in all I realy enjoy this weapon.  And the fact of having a weightless Greatsword is neat too.  And the graphics are nice, looks like a longsword of etheareal energy.</p>&nbsp;<br>Baron Anarus Silverstar<br>Knight of Mithanial Marr<br>Elder of Quintara Qhoenix<br>_________________________<br>Soulast Soulstar<br>Beguiler of Tunare<br>Elder of Quintara Qhoenix</td></td></tr>
